  "texts": [
    "We briefed them on the study and sent each interested staff member a copy of the standard Participant Information Sheet and Consent form.",
    "The study received ethics approval from the University's STEM College Human Ethics Advisory Network (ref. 26253).",
    "Staff who participated were asked to complete a questionnaire and return it to the research team.",
    "We used this method of an open-ended question survey to minimise interruptions to their busy schedules, and it was the best approach to obtain answers to questions in which we were interested in terms of staff time and efficiency.",
    "The data were analysed using the NVivo 12 software package."
  ],
